    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 14th level, the flamboyancy of your bombs can no longer be ignored, piercing through any defenses that would usually counteract them. Your <em><strong>Cacophony Bombs</strong></em> now ignore resistance and treat immunity as resistance. Additionally, whenever you apply a <em><strong>Cacophony Bomb</strong></em> to your <em><strong>Cacophony Weapon</strong></em> you may change your weapon's damage to your bomb's damage for the next attack made while the bomb is still applied to the weapon.</p>",
